              </div>
              <p class="h4 font-semibold">
                Full body sequence including neck, chest, abdomen, legs, arms, face
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p>Indications include:</p>
              <p class="text-base-content/80">
                Lymphedema, Lipedema, Chronic Health Issues, Post-Traumatic Injury Edema,
                post-surgical edema from DIEP flap reconstruction, mastectomy, lumpectomy,
                gender-affirming surgery, and any other surgeries that are cancer-related.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="card-actions justify-center mt-auto">
              <a
                href="https://booksy.com/en-us/1554807_lymphatic-specialists-of-madison_massage_39663_madison#ba_s=sh_1"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="btn btn-primary w-full"
              >
                Book Now
              </a>
            </div>
          </Card>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <ThemedSection
      id="manual-lymphatic-drainage-cta"
      class="bg-radial-[at_20%_25%] from-primary/15 to-accent/15 to-95%"
    >
      <div class="wrapper container lg:max-w-screen-xl mx-auto">
        <div
          class="flex flex-col items-center gap-(--site-padding-md) max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center"
        >
          <h2 class="max-w-2xl lsa lsa-slide-up no-repeat">
            To schedule a Manual Lymphatic Drainage session:
          </h2>

          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 justify-center">
            <div class="lsa lsa-slide-up no-repeat">
              <a
                href="https://booksy.com/en-us/1554807_lymphatic-specialists-of-madison_massage_39663_madison#ba_s=sh_1"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="btn btn-primary"
              >
                Book Now
              </a>
            </div>
            <div class="lsa lsa-slide-up no-repeat">
              <a href="tel:(608) 358-2082" class="btn btn-dash"> Call (608) 358-2082 </a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Important Notes -->
          <p class="text-sm mx-auto lsa lsa-slide-up no-repeat">
            <em
              ><span class="text-primary">*</span><span class="font-nuckle-semibold">
                A couple of points to remember when booking your Manual Lymphatic Drainage session:</span
              >

              A couple of points to remember when booking your Manual Lymphatic Drainage session:
              Make sure you schedule at a time that you are able to go home and rest for the
              remainder of the day, as most patients often feel very relaxed after a session. Also,
              it is not recommended that you come after a big meal. The deep abdominal work can get
              uncomfortable right after eating. Please also remember to stay hydrated before and
              after sessions.
            </em>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </ThemedSection>
  </main>
</Layout>
